name: M18 FUEL™ UTILITY FENCING STAPLER
description: Our MILWAUKEE® M18 FUEL Utility Fencing Stapler delivers unmatched performance in a completely battery-powered solution. By leveraging our Nitrogen Air Spring technology, POWERSTATE™ Brushless motor, and REDLINK™ Intelligence, this stapler delivers the power to seat staples into the toughest Utility Pole and Fence Post Materials

name: M18™ Orbital 1/4 Sheet Sander
description: Designed for the professional carpenter, remodeler, and general contractor; our M18™ Orbital 1/4 Sheet Sander is optimized for performance and productivity on the jobsite. This M18™ Orbital 1/4 Sheet Sander offers unmatched power at 13K Max OPM and class-leading dust collection to replace your corded unit.

name: M12 Cable Stapler
description: Our MILWAUKEE® M12 Cable Stapler delivers unmatched stapling performance in the most compact battery-powered solution leading to a faster, more efficient rough-in process. Our compact, lightweight design provides users with access to tight stud bays and improved ergonomics when stapling overhead or during difficult-to-reach situations.

name: M18 FUEL™ 15mm Random Orbital Polisher
description: Our M18™ FUEL™ 15mm Random Orbital Polisher is the most powerful cordless polisher on the market. By harnessing the power, performance, and run-time of M18™ FUEL™ technology, this tool delivers corded performance while providing you with the freedom to work anywhere.

name: 11pc Metric Combination Wrench Set
description: Our MILWAUKEE® 11 Piece Metric Combination Wrench Set delivers maximum torque and ultimate user comfort. Our MAX BITE™ Open-End Grip improves the wrench's grip on nuts and bolts, and the geometry reduces rounding and stripping. MAX BITE™ offers 25% More Torque than competitive wrench designs.

name: 11pc SAE Combination Wrench Set
description: Our MILWAUKEE® 11 Piece SAE Combination Wrench Set delivers maximum torque and ultimate user comfort. Our MAX BITE™ Open-End Grip improves the wrench's grip on nuts and bolts, and the geometry reduces rounding and stripping. Our MAX BITE™ offers 25% More Torque than competitive wrench designs.

name: 25pc 1/4 Drive Metric & SAE Ratchet and Socket Set with FOUR FLAT™ SIDES
description: Our MILWAUKEE® 11 Piece SAE Combination Wrench Set delivers maximum torque and ultimate user comfort. Our MAX BITE™ Open-End Grip improves the wrench's grip on nuts and bolts, and the geometry reduces rounding and stripping. Our MAX BITE™ offers 25% More Torque than competitive wrench designs.

name: 28oz Milled Face Framing Hammer
description: Our 28oz. Milled Face Framing Hammer is designed for the Best Driving Performance. Its precision balanced design provides strong and smooth striking power, while the I-beam handle is designed to withstand bending.

name: M18™ TOP-OFF™ 175W POWER SUPPLY
description: Our M18™ TOP-OFF™ 175W Power Supply delivers faster simultaneous power to personal devices and small electronics. Attach any M18™ battery to provide continuous power or recharge devices with (1) AC 120V outlet, (1) USB-C PD port, and (1) USB-A port.

name: M18™ & M12™ Super Charger
description: The M18™ & M12™ Super Charger charges batteries up to 4X faster than standard Milwaukee chargers, massively reducing downtime and maximizing productivity. The charger accepts all M18™ & M12™ batteries, providing an upgrade for both M18™ & M12™ systems.

name: M18™ REDLITHIUM™ HIGH OUTPUT™ CP3.0 Battery
description: The M18™ REDLITHIUM™ HIGH OUTPUT™ CP3.0 Battery Pack provides 50% more power and runs 50% cooler vs M18™ REDLITHIUM™ CP battery packs. This increased performance results in the same power and runtime of a M18™ REDLITHIUM™ XC battery in a lighter and more compact package.

name: M18™ REDLITHIUM™ HIGH OUTPUT™ CP3.0 Battery 2-Pack
description: The M18™ REDLITHIUM™ HIGH OUTPUT™ CP3.0 Battery Pack provides 50% more power and runs 50% cooler vs M18™ REDLITHIUM™ CP battery packs. This increased performance results in the same power and runtime of a M18™ REDLITHIUM™ XC battery in a lighter and more compact package.
